<section>
<p style="Heading 1"><c props="lang:en-GB"></c><c props="lang:en-US">0.99.1 Changelog</c></p>
<p style="Normal"><c props="lang:en-US">Taking Dom seriously, the next version should be 0.99.1, so this is the changelog for that. Normal caveats apply.</c></p>
<p style="Heading 2">Paul Anguiano</p>
<p style="Normal">FreeBSD fixes.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">A. Alper Atici</p>
<p style="Normal">Turkish localisation.</p>
<p style="Normal">Work on help files.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Piotr Banski</p>
<p style="Normal">Polish localisation update and tool tips.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">David Chart</p>
<p style="Normal">Work on help files.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Kenneth Christiansen</p>
<p style="Normal">Danish localisation update.</p>
<p style="Normal">Perl script to convert the docs to HTML.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">John Clark</p>
<p style="Normal">Fix to CSS export.</p>
<p style="Normal">Bug fixes to XHTML export, bugs 2002, 2288, 2290, 2337.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Jeremy Davis</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed crashes on startup in BiDi build.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Andrew Dunbar</p>
<p style="Normal">Work on translator plug in.</p>
<p style="Normal">Added languages to AbiWord.</p>
<p style="Normal">Swiss High German localisation.</p>
<p style="Normal">Initial support for Assamese.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Hubert Figuiere</p>
<p style="Normal">Bug fixes, including 2327, 2328, 2415.</p>
<p style="Normal">Removed all CR from the source code.</p>
<p style="Normal">Mac OSX build fixes. AbiWord almost builds under Cocoa. The built binary can only segfault, but it's progress.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed Solaris build and packaging.</p>
<p style="Normal">RTF bookmark import and export.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixes to cut and paste.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fix to libjpeg build.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Ram√≥n Flores</p>
<p style="Normal">Upgrade to galician spellcheck.</p>
<p style="Normal">Work on galician localisation.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Anthony Fok</p>
<p style="Normal">Chinese translations (both traditional and simplified), courtesy of Thiz Linux.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fix problem with Null character in labelset header.</p>
<p style="Normal">Work on PostScript output.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Francis Franklin</p>
<p style="Normal">Ability to disable specific plug-ins in autoconf build.</p>
<p style="Normal">Beginnings of an HTML importer plug-in.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fix to XDarwin build.</p>
<p style="Normal">Move AikSaurus into normal plug-in build system, and work on build system.</p>
<p style="Normal">Several fixes to the build system.</p>
<p style="Normal">Mac OSX wrapper for XDarwin AbiWord.</p>
<p style="Normal">Pseudo-browser for XDarwin build.</p>
<p style="Normal">Workaround for a bug in libxml2.</p>
<p style="Normal">Alterations to wv so that it builds as a shared library.</p>
<p style="Normal">Update to plugin build system.</p>
<p style="Normal">Numerous spelling fixes: upgrades to british.hash, and american.hash.</p>
<p style="Normal">Added Brazilian hash files to abispell and fixed AbiWord to use them in the appropriate locale.</p>
<p style="Normal">Big-endian Portuguese dictionary.</p>
<p style="Normal">Update to abispell RPM script.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fix bugs, including 2564.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Tomas Frydrych</p>
<p style="Normal">Fix a crashing bug when printing ttf fonts.</p>
<p style="Normal">BiDi work.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fix a problem with italic text not always displaying or printing properly.</p>
<p style="Normal">More intelligent selection of highlight color.</p>
<p style="Normal">Quote character fixes.</p>
<p style="Normal">Removed redundant drawing of background rectangles.</p>
<p style="Normal">Added hooks for fine-tuning printing.</p>
<p style="Normal">Work on PostScript output.</p>
<p style="Normal">Change Insert Bookmark hotkey. (It was the same as Insert Break.)</p>
<p style="Normal">Added a Delete button to the Insert Bookmark dialog.</p>
<p style="Normal">Patch to wv to fix potential crashes and handle bookmarks.</p>
<p style="Normal">Word bookmark import.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixes to Word hyperlink import.</p>
<p style="Normal">Word page ref import.</p>
<p style="Normal">Work on Word list import.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixes to Word importer.</p>
<p style="Normal">Win32 Go To dialog fix.</p>
<p style="Normal">Work on lists for BiDi build.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed a crashing bug in Go To which happened with incomplete bookmarks.</p>
<p style="Normal">Added a dialog box to the Insert Field dialog, so that Page Reference fields can be inserted.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixes to paragraph preview.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixes for bugs with tabs and indents.</p>
<p style="Normal">Significant changes to layout code to remove the underlying causes of bug 2313.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed a bug with page layout that was causing crashes on exit.</p>
<p style="Normal">Bug fixes, including 665, 1120, 1153, 1198, 1734, 2133, 2324, 2339, 2351, 2499, 2535, 2571.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Martin Gansser</p>
<p style="Normal">Build fixes for HP UX 10.20.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Gabriel Gerhardsson</p>
<p style="Normal">RPM script for abispell.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Alan Horkan</p>
<p style="Normal">favicon.ico for the web site.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Karl Ove Hufthammer</p>
<p style="Normal">Norwegian Nynorsk update.</p>
<p style="Heading 2"><c props="lang:en-US">Marco Innocenti</c></p>
<p style="Normal"><c props="lang:en-US">Italian strings update.</c></p>
<p style="Heading 2">Nikolaj Brandt Jensen</p>
<p style="Normal">Build fixes on Win32.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Will Lachance</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixes to WordPerfect importer.</p>
<p style="Heading 2"><c props="lang:en-US">Dom Lachowicz</c></p>
<p style="Normal"><c props="lang:en-US">Fix to Undo/Redo of atomic actions.</c></p>
<p style="Normal"><c props="lang:en-US">Work on style locking.</c></p>
<p style="Normal"><c props="lang:en-US">Improvement to cut and paste.</c></p>
<p style="Normal"><c props="lang:en-US">wv bug fixes.</c></p>
<p style="Normal"><c props="lang:en-US">Fix BSD spell checking.</c></p>
<p style="Normal"><c props="lang:en-US">Fix page setup bugs.</c></p>
<p style="Normal"><c props="lang:en-US">Find/replace now reports number of changes made.</c></p>
<p style="Normal"><c props="lang:en-US">Started a unix man/nroff export filter. It doesn't </c><c props="font-style:italic; lang:en-US">do</c><c props="font-style:normal; lang:en-US"> anything yet, not even compile.</c></p>
<p style="Normal"><c props="font-style:normal; lang:en-US">Fixes to website.</c></p>
<p style="Normal"><c props="font-style:normal; lang:en-US">Work on GDKPixBuf plugin.</c></p>
<p style="Normal"><c props="font-style:normal; lang:en-US">Build work for GNOME VFS.</c></p>
<p style="Normal"><c props="font-style:normal; lang:en-US">Work on MS Word importer, to handle bookmarks and hyperlinks, and start handling lists, headers and footers, and respecting section properties.</c></p>
<p style="Normal"><c props="font-style:normal; lang:en-US">Fix to import of MS Word images.</c></p>
<p style="Normal"><c props="font-style:normal; lang:en-US">Final work on Word list import.</c></p>
<p style="Normal"><c props="font-style:normal; lang:en-US">Arcane code changes to PD_Document.</c></p>
<p style="Normal"><c props="font-style:normal; lang:en-US">Cross platform mutex class.</c></p>
<p style="Normal"><c props="font-style:normal; lang:en-US">Fix a page type bug in Preferences.</c></p>
<p style="Normal"><c props="font-style:normal; lang:en-US">Bug fixes, including 609, 2413, 2507 (unix), 2509 (unix).</c></p>
<p style="Normal"><c props="lang:en-US">Work on HTML importer.</c></p>
<p style="Normal"><c props="lang:en-US">Work on docs perl script.</c></p>
<p style="Normal"><c props="lang:en-US">Added new toolbar icons.</c></p>
<p style="Heading 2">Patrick Lam</p>
<p style="Normal">Bug fix to columns dialog.</p>
<p style="Normal">Bug fix in fp_PageSize.cpp.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fix to KWord exporter.</p>
<p style="Normal">Removed fp_PageSize::Unit. This made the code difficult to maintain, as it duplicated another function.</p>
<p style="Normal">Bug fixes, including 922 (quick hack), 1360, 1365, 1399, 1932, 2375.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Per Larsson</p>
<p style="Normal">Swedish localisation update.</p>
<p style="Heading 2"><c props="lang:en-US">Marc Maurer</c></p>
