<p style="Normal"><c props="font-style:normal">Work on Free Translate plugin for Win32.</c></p>
<p style="Normal"><c props="font-style:normal">Bug fixes, including 911, 1932 (Win32), 2007, 2040, 2415, 2423, 2424 (Win32), 2507 (Win32), 2509 (Win32), 2510.</c></p>
